                    </div>
                    <span>I ordered this book because I loved "Into the Forest" by Jean Hegland and was steered to this title. I was so disappointed. He writes like a Junior College Creative Writing student. The characters are all one-sided and the story builds to mediocre climax after mediocre climax. Save your money on this one.</span>
                  
              
